sections.Trivia:
- The vehicle in the poster is a 2006 Toyota Corolla Axio [E140].
- The names of the suspects are related to "airports" and "warlords of the Sengoku period"[1] :
Naganobu Itami (伊丹 永信) comes from Itami Airport (伊丹空港) and Oda Nobunaga (織田 信長, 1534-1582) ;
Yasuie Itami (伊丹 靖家) comes from Itami Airport and Tokugawa Ieyasu (徳川 家康, 1543-1616) ;
Chiyoko Itami (伊丹 知代子) comes from Itami Airport and "Takechiyo" (竹千代), a nickname of "Tokugawa Ieyasu" ;
Ichiko Itami (伊丹 市子) comes from the airport and Oichi no Kata (お市の方, 1547-1583).
